text: Khusainovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kadyrgulovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 304 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 41 km from Davlekanovo, 4 km from Kadyrgulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Khusainovo, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
